Subject: [PATCH 251/256] ENGR00293632 G2D: Rewrite G2D library by using PXP

Previous G2D library is written by using GPU 2D. Now rewrite
it by using PXP. Due to PXP hardware limitations, some of the
G2D functions is incomplete. For example, alpha blending,
dithering and etc.

